// AXP_AbortNoMerc=true/false	If set to true, abort the game if the merc is dead and not ressurected.
// AXP_StopFullInv=true/false	Set to true to stop botting if the inventory is full.
// AXP_StartGameDelay=xxxx	Delay before beginning script in ms (1000ms = 1 second). Set a value here if you are
//				having trouble with the script not detecting your merc or other problems
//				at the beginning of the game.
// AXP_MaxGameLength=xxxxx	Maximum game length before aborting, in SECONDS. Set to 0 for infinite game length.
// AXP_SkipCredits=true/false	Set this to true to skip printing the credits.
// AXP_UseConsole=true/false	Set to true to use the 1337 console (Can be toggled on and off in game with "U")
